{"tid":2399030,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"經過琴日象棋個po 我諗到一個圍棋新玩法","createTime":"2021-02-07T19:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T02:17:50.000Z","uid":370062,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68596d5060f2efc387093f8f240f0ff3cf70ff52","tid":2399030,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"就係三人圍棋<br />\n都唔算係啲咩好有諗頭嘅嘢<br />\n純粹多個玩法俾大家參考下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFYk1g0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFYk1g0.jpg&h=b7229e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下子：黑，白，灰輪流下子<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吃子：同原版一樣，冇氣就會俾人食，而且<strong>唔需要</strong>由同一隻色嘅棋圍住先食得。<br />\n例如第一種情況，白棋俾三隻黑棋圍住，得返一口氣，呢個時候灰棋填埋佢最後一口氣，白棋就會被吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二種情況，雖然灰棋行嗰個位冇氣，但係由於白棋會被吃，令灰棋多返口氣，因此灰棋可以咁行食白棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三種情況，灰棋行嗰個位可以同時令黑棋白棋都冇氣，所以佢可以同時食曬兩隻棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勝負：圍得多地贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼目：唔識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之其實都同普通圍棋大同小異，純粹多隻色咁解，亦都可以擴展成四人五人甚至更多，你哋夠腳就得，甚至可以演變成2v2等唔同玩法，2v2我諗到三種玩法，按照下子次序分別為黑白黑白，黑黑白白，黑白灰紅。<br />\n黑白黑白其實同普通行法冇分別，不過同隊嘅兩位玩家冇得交流，所以可能會出現神carry或者老鼠屎嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑黑白白就係同一隻色可以由同隊嘅兩個人連行兩步，諗下都覺得刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑白灰紅係黑灰一隊，白紅一隊，特登分成四隻色嘅唯一目的就係<span class=\"red\">有team kill</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOTX3GX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOTX3GX.jpg&h=e37bcffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即係咁樣，雖然白紅係同隊，但係由於唔同色，所以紅色會team kill咗白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />白色<br />\n好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋大家可以因應情況擴大棋盤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我諗到嘅淨係得咁多<br />\n歡迎大家補充或者提出疑問同bug<br />\n仲有我會整合下象棋個po有啲咩高質可行嘅玩法<br />\n遲啲再開個po向大家介紹返"},{"pid":"184468a85dc1a72b17ee7349ae5a5397716b95ed","tid":2399030,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:10:28.000Z","msg":"唔識 但好似幾得意 lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3309924f7a81763253dda5d5ce2c3b6a1f84c3ad","tid":2399030,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"184468a85dc1a72b17ee7349ae5a5397716b95ed","tid":2399030,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:10:28.000Z","msg":"唔識 但好似幾得意 lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:12:50.000Z","msg":"圍棋幾好玩，有興趣可以學下，不過缺點係一局太嘥時間，好易冇耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a53bc504265a8b396ef58bdc34c9940f2db9bf4","tid":2399030,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:32:08.000Z","msg":"諗落幾好玩 應該會有新行法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81b28f1f35061aead6494e3867e1d43272b74c2","tid":2399030,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:57:23.000Z","msg":"但圍棋九成時間都唔會提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係角落頭互相佔地 慢慢攻到去中央<br />\n三個人真係唔知點玩"},{"pid":"95c6e6bc6f4a15d09940a0171504e63d1e9799a2","tid":2399030,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e81b28f1f35061aead6494e3867e1d43272b74c2","tid":2399030,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T21:57:23.000Z","msg":"但圍棋九成時間都唔會提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係角落頭互相佔地 慢慢攻到去中央<br />\n三個人真係唔知點玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T02:17:50.000Z","msg":"照玩，三個人互有攻守仲刺激"}]}